<br>
In every computer role playing game I played, if a &quot;fighter&quot; type class was available, I played that one.<br>
<br>
In EQ, I never even had to think twice about what class my main would be.  I play a Warrior because that's my favorite class type in any fantasy game.<br>
<br>
Imagine my shock when I found out that my vision of a Warrior and Verant's &quot;Vision&quot;(tm) of a Warrior were far, far different from each other.  <br>
<br>
Still, I'm just not into playing a spellcaster, and I like the Warrior concept (even if Verant's implementation of it sucks), so that's what I play.<br>
<br>
Just my opinion, your mileage may vary.  :-)<br>
