<br>
My enchanter has been level 37 since Kunark was released, and my rogue is now 61 only because I haven't had very much time to play EQ for the last year or so.<br>
<br>
The main reason I play my warrior (level 46 now) is because when I have a chance to play EQ I don't have the time to be in game long enough to attend guild raids, etc. So, I solo and join the occasional group with the little gnome warrior. <br>
<br>
I think I've had more fun with this little warrior than I've had with any character in a long time.  And... I'm very tempted to start a frog warrior just for the 'halibut'. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
